long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Take your home cooking to the next level with Foodify's new tab extension, designed to offer you a plethora of diverse recipes, ranging from classic dishes to contemporary culinary innovations.

By clicking "Add to chrome", I accept and agree to installing the Foodify extension and setting Chrome New Tab search provider to Microsoft Bing as described by the service in terms of use https://foooodify.com/terms-and-conditions/ and Privacy Policy: https://foooodify.com/privacy-policy/
